🍦Yummiest scent from KAYALI 🍨! Was super excited to receive this Yum Pistachio Gelato 33 from kayali and skeepers_us 💚 TYSM!😘

Key Notes: 
Pistachio Gelato
Hazelnut 
Sweet Rum 
Whipped Cream 
Marshmallow 
Cotton Candy 

One spray is enough to experience this yummy fragrance. Tbh I didn’t know what to expect from a ‘Pistachio’ scent, but this one is a keeper! It’s delicious but not overly sweet, dries down to a fresh powdery scent with a hint of the sweetness. I don’t usually go for sweet scents but this has the right balance and not overpowering. Too strong scents trigger my rhinitis but not this. 

Beautiful unique scent added to my small fragrance collection. Recently bought a perfume at Sephora (famous brand) but then my husband said I smell like everyone else at the mall🤣. Let’s just say I won’t smell like majority of the people when I wear this perfume. It’s been 9 hours since i sprayed it on me and i can still smell it although faint now. I could see myself wearing this day or night and perfect this spring!

What is your fave fragrance this spring?🌸

It’s one of those fragrance you just CAN’T get enough of. It’s the perfect combination of sweet and nutty gourmand notes. It’s playful and flirtatious and yet intense at the same time. She’s the ultimate mood booster that honestly makes me feel sooooo happy, kinda like that first bite of your fave dessert.
—————————————————————————— 
The Technology

For all you fragrance nerds out there, you may already be clued in on STT technology, which was a key component in us making this fragrance. It’s the art of expressing tastes in fragrances, a technique drawn by the expertise of flavorists for perfumers and their creations. The ingredients give texture, evoke appetizing emotion, and add another layer of innovation to new fragrances. It’s what makes the scent soooo special and truly tantalizing.

Joining KAYALI's ranks of intoxicatingly addictive range of scents, Yum Pistachio Gelato | 33 Eau de Parfum Intense is a sweet tooth lover's dream fragrance.
This opens with mouthwatering facets of hazelnut and pistachio blended with rum for a tantalising first impression. In the heart, beautiful white peony creates a rosy, honey-like effect while muguet helps maintain the luxurious balance of sweetness, freshness and sophistication. As the dry down continues, enjoy a delicious overdose of whipped cream, fluffy marshmallow and creamy sandalwood for an insanely delectable gourmand fragrance.
—————————————————————————— 
HOW TO USE

Spritz a couple of times on your hair or pulse points (or both) to leave an addictive trail of fragrance throughout the day.

Spray your fragrance into your hairbrush before brushing your hair.

Spray the scent on your hair towel before drying your hair, the result is a subtle hint of the fragrance that will follow you around all day.
——————————————————————————
Mona’s Perfume Tips & Tricks

Spray Yum Pistachio Gelato | 33 EDP on your pulse points (inside wrists, behind the knees, the center of the chest, nape of the neck, behind the ears) as well as on your clothes for a more powerful scent trail.

For even longer wear, moisturize your pulse points with balm or lotion, like our KAYALI Vanilla | 28 Hand Cream, $15, before spritzing on your body. The rich vanilla scent is the ultimate base.

For a delicate diffusion, spray on your hair towel before drying your hair or directly onto your hairbrush prior to styling.

Joining KAYALI's ranks of intoxicatingly addictive range of scents, Yum Pistachio Gelato | 33 Eau de Parfum Intense is a sweet tooth lover's dream fragrance.

This opens with mouthwatering facets of hazelnut and pistachio blended with rum for a tantalising first impression. In the heart, beautiful white peony creates a rosy, honey-like effect while muguet helps maintain the luxurious balance of sweetness, freshness and sophistication. As the dry down continues, enjoy a delicious overdose of whipped cream, fluffy marshmallow and creamy sandalwood for an insanely delectable gourmand fragrance.
—————————————————————————— 
HOW TO USE

Spritz a couple of times on your hair or pulse points (or both) to leave an addictive trail of fragrance throughout the day.

Spray your fragrance into your hairbrush before brushing your hair.

Spray the scent on your hair towel before drying your hair, the result is a subtle hint of the fragrance that will follow you around all day.

HOW TO USE

Spritz a couple of times on your hair or pulse points (or both) to leave an addictive trail of fragrance throughout the day.

Spray your fragrance into your hairbrush before brushing your hair.

Spray the scent on your hair towel before drying your hair, the result is a subtle hint of the fragrance that will follow you around all day.

I’m going to pass the mic to Olivier to describe the juice this time, “The fragrance begins with mouth-watering facets of hazelnut and pistachio blended with rum for a charismatic addiction. In the heart, we used the beautiful white peony for a rosy, honey-like effect and muguet to maintain the perfect balance of sweetness, freshness, and sophistication.” One word… YUM!!
It’s one of those fragrance you just CAN’T get enough of. It’s the perfect combination of sweet and nutty gourmand notes. It’s playful and flirtatious and yet intense at the same time. She’s the ultimate mood booster that honestly makes me feel sooooo happy, kinda like that first bite of your fave dessert.

Mona’s Perfume Tips & Tricks

Spray Yum Pistachio Gelato | 33 EDP on your pulse points (inside wrists, behind the knees, the center of the chest, nape of the neck, behind the ears) as well as on your clothes for a more powerful scent trail.

For even longer wear, moisturize your pulse points with balm or lotion, like our KAYALI Vanilla | 28 Hand Cream, $15, before spritzing on your body. The rich vanilla scent is the ultimate base.

For a delicate diffusion, spray on your hair towel before drying your hair or directly onto your hairbrush prior to styling.

Mona’s Perfume Tips & Tricks

Spray Yum Pistachio Gelato | 33 EDP on your pulse points (inside wrists, behind the knees, the center of the chest, nape of the neck, behind the ears) as well as on your clothes for a more powerful scent trail.

For even longer wear, moisturize your pulse points with balm or lotion, like our KAYALI Vanilla | 28 Hand Cream, $15, before spritzing on your body. The rich vanilla scent is the ultimate base.

For a delicate diffusion, spray on your hair towel before drying your hair or directly onto your hairbrush prior to styling.

BEHIND THE SCENT

A Quote from Mona

I wanted to combine my two favorite indulgences, fragrance & gelato! Ever since I can remember, ice cream has been my favorite food and always my #1 choice when asked what would be my last meal! In 2014, I went on a trip to Rome with my sister Alya and discovered pistachio gelato -I have been OBSESSED ever since! Just like the dreamy dessert, I wanted to create something that made me feel yummy, happy and irresistible! Working with Olivier Cresp, (a world- renowned perfumer who is often credited as the “father” of gourmand fragrances) and his son, Sebastien, was SO exciting. With every delicious spritz, you’ll feel like YOU ARE the dessert!

Questi scatti sono stati un duro lavoro ma ora sono una grande soddisfazione!
Chi mi conosce sa che non sono mai soddisfatta e che cerco sempre di migliorare.
Ero solita scoraggiarmi con frasi:" eh ma non sono come o non arriverò mai a..".
Mi sentivo io contro un mondo di persone che, come me, hanno reso il makeup protagonista dei loro profili.
Mi chiedevo sempre:" Cosa può un pesce in un oceano così grande?"
In passato avrei risposto con "nulla", ma ad oggi dico:" fa il suo ed è questo ciò che conta"
Non bisogna impressionare gli altri, bisogna rendere fieri se stessi.
Se vi sentite come mi sono senti io, prima di questa soddisfazione, vi dico:" non mollate!".
Le strade dritte sono per chi vive la vita con i paraocchi, quelle tortuose sono per chi la vita la vive guardandola su più prospettive.

¡Buenas noches! ✨

Hoy vengo a hablaros de una paleta que probablemente la mayoría ya conozcáis, porque en su momento se puso muy de moda cuando salió al mercado 🥹 Se trata de la paleta Rose Quartz de hudabeauty 💘 Yo me resistía a hacerme con ella pero la conseguí rebajadisima en sephora (me parece que a 45 euros estaba 😱) y no me pude aguantar más 🙊

Os cuento un poco: 

Es una paleta inspirada en la piedra favorita de Huda, el cuarzo rosa 💖 Está compuesta por 18 sombras en diferentes acabados: 

✨ 8 tonos mate ✨
✨3 tonos metálicos ultrabrillantes✨
✨3 tonos metalizados perlados✨
✨ 3 tonos en crema veteados✨
✨ 1 tono hibrido (el de bolitas que no le gusta a nadie 😅)✨

Si deslizáis podeis ver todos los tonos ( he intentado hacer swatches decentes 🫶🏻🤣), como podéis ver la pigmentación es increíble y es que las sombras se difuminan como la mantequilla y tienen una duración brutal 💖 Nunca había tenido una paleta grande de Huda y estoy encantadisima porque puedes hacer looks más diarios y luego utilizar algunos de los tonos metalizados para hacer algo más potente 🤩

Estoy gratamente sorprendida con la calidad de esta paleta y, aunque algunos tonos no van mucho conmigo (el de las bolitas 😢) me parece que es una paleta muy completa y que le podria encajar a cualquiera 💖

La tenéis disponible en sephora_spain a un precio de 70€ pero la he visto muchas veces con descuentos grandes como el mio, así que si la veis corred 🏃🏻‍♀️🤣 Ah! Y obviamente también está en la propia web de hudabeauty 

Contadme, ¿la habéis probado? ¿Tenéis paletas de Huda Beauty? ¡Os leo! 🙈

Wat betekent techniek?

 In tegenstelling tot de permanente en kunstmatige tatoeages die in het verleden zijn gemaakt, is de haartechniek een driedimensionale haartekening gemaakt met semi-permanente verf op de huid, niet te onderscheiden van natuurlijk haar.

Hoe wordt microblading gedaan?
 Bij microblading-applicatie;  Met de plantaardige permanente make-up kleurstof geproduceerd volgens het permanente make-up proces, worden micro-incisies in de vorm van haar gemaakt onder de diepte (epidermis) met behulp van steriele wegwerpnaalden.  In het toepassingsgebied wordt een driedimensionaal haarbeeld gecreëerd.

Fragrance Layering 101:
Layering is all about finding scent combinations that you love, so experiment, and don’t be afraid to try different combinations. Spray scents in order of intensity so they don’t get overpowered. Stronger scents first, and lighter ones last

Tips for long-lasting perfume:

Spray, don’t rub.

Keep your perfume at room temperature, not in the bathroom.

Think: cleanse, moisturize, fragrance! Moist skin helps the scent ‘stick’.
